<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jordan luipang huih hat lakah,
 Ding in, ka en zing hi;
 Kanaan gam hawih kipahna gam,
 Ka kumsawt chenna ding.

[V2]
 Chawl hitiu zie gam hawih leh nuom achun,
 Gal lehlam gam hing zing mun achun;
 Mosi leh Belam No lasai tiu dantak leh,
 Isu kawmah cheng den tai tiu.

[V3]
 2. Zie gam nuom hawih tak chung achun,
 Kumsawt vak chuh a um;
 Pathien Chapa'n kumkhuo'n vaihawm,
 Thimna A nawh mang tai.

[V4]
 3. Bangtik gam nuom chuh ka tung dem?
 Kumsawt vangsak changin?
 Bangtik ka pa mel ka mu dem?
 A angah ka chawl dem?

[V5]
 4. Ka lung kipahnan a dim hi,
 Ziehin cheng sawt puo'ng ka;
 Jordan luipi kinawk mahleh,
 Lau lo in kai ingka.</lyrics>
<title>ON JORDAN'S STORMY BANKS</title>
</song>